---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | David Glass" description="Privacy policy for the David Glass campaign website.">
  
  <article class="py-24 bg-white min-h-[70vh]">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg prose-navy">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-navy mb-8 border-b-4 border-gold inline-block pb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <p>Last updated: March 2026</p>
      
      <p>
        The David Glass Campaign ("we," "our," or "us") operates the website electdavidglass.com (the "Site"). We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal data we collect.
      </p>

      <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Sign up for our email newsletter (Name, Email).</li>
        <li>Submit a form through our Contact page (Name, Email, Phone Number, Subject, Message).</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>The information we collect is used to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide you with updates regarding Precinct 4, county business, and community events.</li>
        <li>Respond to your direct inquiries or comments submitted via the Contact form.</li>
        <li>Improve our website and constituent communications.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will never sell, rent, or lease your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h3>3. Cookies and Analytics</h3>
      <p>We use privacy-respecting analytics (such as Cloudflare Web Analytics) to understand how visitors use our site. This tool does not use cookies or collect personally identifiable or tracking information across different websites.</p>

      <h3>4. Communication Preferences</h3>
      <p>If you have subscribed to our email updates, you may opt out at any time by clicking the "unsubscribe" link included at the bottom of every email we send.</p>

      <h3>5. Contact Us</h3>
      <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
      <p>
        David Glass, Bastrop County Commissioner, Precinct 4<br/>
        804 Pecan St<br/>
        Bastrop, TX 78602<br/>
        (512) 581-7100
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

</Base>
